title: Still ahvent gotten any gifts is somthing wrong?
body: It says it all in the title

replies.body: Nothing is wrong, and you won't get all the gifts at the same time.  Per our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-) we're still rolling out gifts.  Just hang tight!
The gifts are not yet done being distributed. They are being handed out one by one, not all at the same time. If you don't receive them by the 23rd, you can submit a support ticket.
